OL,7,FA toddler's mother installed a spy
OL,8,Fcamera above his cot because she was
OL,9,F"concerned" about her partner months
OL,10,Fbefore he allegedly inflicted a fatal
OL,11,Fhead injury, a jury was told.
OL,13,FPaula Roberts, 41, left her son
OL,14,FCharlie, aged one year and 10 months,
OL,15,Fin the sole care of her partner
OL,16,FChristopher Stockton, 38, at her
OL,17,FDarlington home while she went for an
OL,18,Feye test, Teesside Crown Court heard
OL,19,Fon Wednesday (14 November).
