OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FAfter a night of playing on his Xbox
OL,8,Fand watching TV, Stockton was sleep
OL,9,Fdeprived and within minutes of Roberts
OL,10,Fleaving, he had dialled 999 just after
OL,11,F9am because the toddler, he said, had
OL,12,Fgone "floppy" for no good reason.
OL,14,FStockton, who was not Charlie's
OL,15,Ffather, is accused of inflicting a
OL,16,Fserious brain injury which could not
OL,17,Fbe survived.
OL,26,@tD@FOUtD@MO]
