OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FNicholas Lumley KC, prosecuting, said:
OL,8,F"In a very short time, for that's all
OL,9,Fit takes to lose one's temper, he must
OL,10,Fhave assaulted Charlie by shaking or
OL,11,Fthrowing him with considerable force."
OL,13,FHe denies murder and a charge of child
OL,14,Fneglect.
OL,16,FRoberts is also charged with child
OL,17,Fneglect, which she denies.
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@fO]
