OL,7,FCharlie suffered a number of bruises
OL,8,Fand injuries in the weeks and months
OL,9,Fprior to his death in January, the
OL,10,Fcourt heard.
OL,12,FMr Lumley said Roberts expressed
OL,13,Fconcerns in August 2023 to her brother
OL,14,Fabout Stockton, who had known Charlie
OL,15,Ffor around 10 months prior to his
OL,16,Fdeath.
OL,18,FMr Lumley said: "As August progressed,
OL,19,Fit seems that the relationship between
OL,20,FChristopher Stockton and Paula Roberts
OL,21,Fbecame a little rocky.
OL,26,@zD@QOU
