OL,3,CMother of toddler who suffered fatal
OL,4,Chead injury installed spy camera, jury
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"They resolved to stay together but
OL,8,Fthere were tensions.
OL,10,F"Christopher Stockton spoke of
OL,11,Fproblems at work and with his ex-wife.
OL,13,F"At the very end of August 2023, Paula
OL,14,FRoberts bought a spy camera."
OL,16,FMr Lumley said she concealed it in a
OL,17,Fpotted plant above Charlie's cot.
OL,19,F"She told her brother that she was
OL,20,Fconcerned about Christopher Stockton
OL,21,Fand Charlie," Mr Lumley said.
