OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FIn May last year, Charlie was taken to
OL,8,FDarlington Memorial Hospital with a
OL,9,Fnumber of bruises to his face, which
OL,10,Fhis mother explained was the result of
OL,11,Ffalls.
OL,13,FMr Lumley said meetings with social
OL,14,Fservices were held out of concern for
OL,15,Fthe toddler but at that stage, his
OL,16,Finjuries were not thought to have been
OL,17,Fcaused deliberately.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/12
