OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe jury was shown a photo that
OL,8,FStockton took in December of Charlie
OL,9,Fstanding in the corner of a room
OL,10,Fdecorated for Christmas, because he
OL,11,Fhad been "naughty", after the adult
OL,12,Fsaid the child had hit him.
OL,14,FAs well as a number of bruises he
OL,15,Fsuffered in his last months, Charlie
OL,16,Fsustained a painful injury to the base
OL,17,Fof his private parts, the court heard.
OL,26,@sD@JOUsD@RO]
