OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FWhen her brother noticed Charlie had
OL,8,Fbruised ears, Roberts told him the
OL,9,Ftoddler had been sleepwalking and she
OL,10,Fhad found him resting in a toy box.
OL,12,FMr Lumley said pre-school children
OL,13,Frarely sleepwalk.
OL,15,FMr Lumley said: "The prosecution case
OL,16,Fis that there are too many incidents
OL,17,Fof bruising for it not to have been
OL,18,Fthe result of neglect."
OL,20,FCharlie suffered a catastrophic head
OL,21,Finjury on 12 January.
