OL,7,FMr Lumley said: "What happened to
OL,8,FCharlie once his mother had closed the
OL,9,Fdoor on him was no accident, much as
OL,10,Fit may have been quickly and bitterly
OL,11,Fregretted."
OL,13,FRoberts wept as a recording of
OL,14,FStockton's 999 call was played in
OL,15,Fcourt, in which he repeatedly said
OL,16,F"Come on mate" and "wakey wakey" to
OL,17,Fthe little boy, who was not breathing.
