OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe toddler died in hospital the next
OL,8,Fday and post-mortem tests on his brain
OL,9,Ffound widespread bleeding.
OL,11,FA separate expert found bleeding
OL,12,Fwithin and around his eyes, the
OL,13,Fprosecution said.
OL,15,F"There was no natural disease which
OL,16,Fmight account for those injuries and
OL,17,Ffindings," Mr Lumley said.
OL,19,F"They were not the result of a normal
OL,20,Fbump or fall.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@JO]{D@AOU
