OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"The cause of death, therefore, must
OL,8,Fhave been the application of severe
OL,9,Fforce to Charlie, causing his head to
OL,10,Frotate or be thrown about."
OL,12,FMr Lumley said Stockton's case will be
OL,13,Fthat he simply did not cause Charlie's
OL,14,Fdeath and he did not neglect him.
OL,16,FRoberts will say that injuries her son
OL,17,Fsuffered were the result of "everyday
OL,18,Fexistence" and not inflicted by her,
OL,19,Fthe jury was told.
OL,21,FThe case was adjourned until Monday.
